    "body": "This is a good addition, only part I have issue with is the naming, I'd prefer any name that does not have the \"factory\" name in it. I'd prefer something that does not requires the user to know what is a factory or how does a factory applies here.\r\n\r\nThe best one I could come up with is `createAlgoliaClient`, open to other suggestions.",
